---
title: Easy Sri Lankan Pulled Beef & Veggie Curry with Garlic Rice & Crushed Peanuts
description: This creamy coconut pulled beef curry will add the spice you never knew you needed to your night. It's filled to the brim with
bright veggies and finished with a sprinkling of flair from the crushed peanuts.
